* {{tcond|If the player lost the letter:}}
** '''Player:''' I seem to have lost the letter of recommendation that you stamped for me.
** '''Curator Haig Halen:''' Yes, I saw you drop it as you walked off last time. Here it is.
** '''Player:''' Thanks!
** {{tact|continues}}
* {{tcond|If the player still has the letter:}}
** '''Curator Haig Halen:''' I see you still have that letter I stamped for you. Why don't you run it back to the Examiner at the Exam Centre?
** {{tact|continues}}
* {{tcond|If the player still has another unstamped letter:}}
** '''Player:''' I have another letter here; could you stamp it for me again?
** '''Curator Haig Halen:''' You've already given me one of those! But... ok, give it here...
** '''Player:''' Thanks!
** {{tact|continues}}
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
